text: Nikolskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Nikolo-Komarovsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 793 as of 2010. There are 20 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Nikolskoye, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast
